commit.message:
Updated test CA and issued certificates.  Included key file for CA, so
that others can update it if they wish or issue other test certificates.
This is a TEST CA for testing ONLY.  Use accordingly!
Re-instated proxy test otherwise this breaks the code if no proxy is set.
Use README as long_description to avoid duplication
Fix test with subject alt name
Merging in fixes for subject alt name handling
Preparing 0.5.0 release - fix for certs with more than 64 subject alt names

Updated tests to explicitly include subject alt names test.  Tested with
remote peer with > 64 subject alt names

Fix to subject alt name class variable to make byte type for correct
matching for Python 3.
Make sure to exclude build dir
Move docker file into test area
Merge branch 'jayvdb-travis-ci' into devel - added travis yaml
Updated the Python releases to try
Merge branch 'travis-ci' of https://github.com/jayvdb/ndg_httpsclient into jayvdb-travis-ci
